HEADWORD: butterflyfish
<hw>butterflyfish</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>tropical gurnardlike fish with
huge fanlike pectoral fins for underwater gliding; unrelated to
searobins.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> flying gurnard, flying robin.</syn>⟦br⟧
